TITLE: Implementing a Custom Seed Source in Knex.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a custom seed source class in Knex.js. The `MySeedSource` class defines the `getSeeds` and `getSeed` methods, which control the retrieval of seed names and the execution of seed logic, respectively. An instance of this class is then passed to the `knex.seed.run` method to execute the seeds.
