TITLE: Nested Join with Knex.js
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates a nested join statement in Knex.js using a function within the 'on' clause. It joins 'users' and 'accounts' tables, linking them based on either 'accounts.id' matching 'users.account_id' or 'accounts.owner_id' matching 'users.id' using nested 'on' clauses.
SOURCE: https://github.com/knex/documentation/blob/main/src/guide/query-builder.md#_snippet_134

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
