SOURCE: https://github.com/knex/documentation/blob/main/src/guide/index.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const knex = require('knex')({
  client: 'pg',
  version: '7.2',
  connection: {
    host : '127.0.0.1',
    port : 5432,
    user : 'your_database_user',
    password : 'your_database_password',
    database : 'myapp_test'
  }
});
```

