TITLE: Raw Query with Array Binding - Knex.js
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to use array bindings in raw queries by manually constructing the placeholder string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/knex/documentation/blob/main/src/guide/raw.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
