TITLE: Knex.js Configuration with Mixed JS and MJS
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet demonstrates a Knex.js configuration file using the `.mjs` extension with migrations using `.js` extensions.  It specifies the `loadExtensions` property to load `.js` files for migrations when using ESM.  This configuration allows to combine different file types for seeds/migrations and knexfile.
