TITLE: Raw Group By Clause with Knex.js
DESCRIPTION: Adds a raw SQL group by clause to the query using Knex.js. This groups the sales data by year with rollup to include summary rows.
SOURCE: https://github.com/knex/documentation/blob/main/src/guide/query-builder.md#_snippet_164

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
knex.select('year', knex.raw('SUM(profit)'))
  .from('sales')
  .groupByRaw('year WITH ROLLUP')
```

